reviewText: This is NOT about the movie...It's different movie posted by Amazon under 'Bade Dilawala' 1983.. This movie is a sunil shetty movie made in 1998 and not the rishi kapoor movie made in 1983, as it shows in the photo... wrong upload by amazon
Okay - it's a story! Not mesmerizing or captivating! Sufficiently said and sit through it for 3 hours if you have nothing better to do!!
